      <title>Tor Investment 为亚洲私人信贷基金筹集 3.1 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/tor-investment-raises-310-million-for-asia-private-credit-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合创始人兼投资组合经理克里斯托弗·米科什 (Christopher Mikosh) 表示，总部位于香港的另类信贷管理公司 Tor Investment Management 已为其第三支亚洲机会主义私人信贷基金筹集了 3.1 亿美元，旨在利用该资产类别日益受欢迎的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/tor-investment-raises-310-million-for-asia-private-credit-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
